#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.contactus
msgid ""
"Contact us about anything related to our company or services.<br/>We'll do "
"our best to get back to you as soon as possible."
msgstr ""
"Entre em contato conosco sobre qualquer assunto relacionado à nossa empresa "
"ou aos nossos serviços. <br/>Faremos o possível para responder o mais rápido "
"possível."

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model:product.template,name:agriculture_shop.product_product_9_product_template
msgid "Cucumber Seeds"
msgstr "Sementes de Pepino"

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model:product.template,description_sale:agriculture_shop.product_product_9_product_template
msgid ""
"Cucumber seeds are the first step to cultivating refreshing and crunchy "
"cucumbers. These tiny seeds harbor the promise of abundant vines and a "
"bountiful harvest, allowing both gardeners and farmers to enjoy the "
"satisfaction of growing this hydrating and versatile vegetable."
msgstr ""
"As sementes de pepino são o primeiro passo para cultivar pepinos frescos e "
"crocantes. Essas sementes minúsculas prometem vinhas abundantes e uma "
"colheita farta, permitindo que jardineiros e agricultores desfrutem da "
"satisfação de cultivar esse vegetal hidratante e versátil."

#. module: agriculture_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:agriculture_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Decide whether to allow sales of <b>out-of-stock\n"
