msgid ""
"Odoo’s <strong>Point of Sale (POS)</strong> system ensures fast and smooth\n"
"            transactions in your agriculturalshop. Whether you sell "
"individual packaged seeds,\n"
"            or bulk pick &amp; mix, Odoo has you covered."
